longBusinessSummary: Impex Ferro Tech Limited manufactures and supplies various ferro alloys in India and internationally. Its ferro alloy products include silico manganese and high and medium carbon ferro manganese for use in making various types of carbon and alloy steels, as well as deoxidation, desulphurization, and refining of steel. Impex Ferro Tech Limited was incorporated in 1995 and is based in Kolkata, India.
